Maggie Han https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maggie_Han 0 Maggie Han (born 1959) is an American actress. Her career began with modeling jobs in the United States and France, and progressed to acting in film and television productions. She is best known for playing Yoshiko Kawashima in The Last Emperor and Cheryl the lawyer in the NBC sitcom Seinfeld. Maggie_Han ( born 1959 ) is an_American_actress .
